OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784839667
OL,3,CNumber of Brits with eating disorders
OL,4,Cnearly trebles in less than 10 years
OL,6,FUK's eating disorder charity, Beat, is
OL,7,Fnow calling on the Government to
OL,8,Fincrease support for people with
OL,9,Feating disorders across the country,
OL,10,FITV News' Caroline Lewis reports
OL,12,FAn estimated 3.5 million people in the
OL,13,FUK are now affected by an eating
OL,14,Fdisorder, according to new figures
OL,15,Ffrom a leading charity, marking a
OL,16,Fsubstantial increase over the past
OL,17,Fdecade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784839667
OL,3,CNumber of Brits with eating disorders
OL,4,Cnearly trebles in less than 10 years
OL,6,FCharity Beat's new data shows a
OL,7,Fsignificant increase in the estimated
OL,8,Fnumber of people living with an eating
OL,9,Fdisorder in the UK, rising from 1.25
OL,10,Fmillion in 2017 to 3.5 million today.
OL,12,FThe figures mean around one in 20
OL,13,Fpeople are affected and suggest eating
OL,14,Fdisorders are far more common than
OL,15,Fpreviously thought, the charity said.
OL,17,FIt has also warned about the lack of
OL,18,Fregulation surrounding weight loss
OL,19,Fdrugs, saying some people with eating
OL,20,Fdisorders have been able to access
OL,21,Fthem with little or no scrutiny.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784839667
OL,3,CNumber of Brits with eating disorders
OL,4,Cnearly trebles in less than 10 years
OL,6,FBeat is now calling on the government
OL,7,Fto increase support for people with
OL,8,Feating disorders across the country.
OL,10,FIt said the future Mental Health
OL,11,FStrategy for England must include a
OL,12,Fspecific focus on eating disorders and
OL,13,Fset out a clear framework for care
OL,14,Fthat regional and local NHS leaders
OL,15,Fare expected to enforce consistently.
OL,17,FThe strategy should include a stepped-
OL,18,Fcare model, where patients are offered
OL,19,Fthe least intrusive interventios, for
OL,20,Feating disorder treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784839667
OL,3,CNumber of Brits with eating disorders
OL,4,Cnearly trebles in less than 10 years
OL,6,FThis approach is designed to provide
OL,7,Ftimely access to effective care that
OL,8,Freflects individual needs, alongside
OL,9,Ftailored support for families and
OL,10,Fcarers, Beat said.
OL,12,FIn a statement Beat's chief executive
OL,13,FVanessa Longley said: "These figures
OL,14,Fshould be a wake-up call. Eating
OL,15,Fdisorders are not a rare condition.
OL,17,F"For years we've heard from people
OL,18,Fwith eating disorders, families,
OL,19,Fclinicians and services that the
OL,20,Fproblem is getting worse.
OL,26,@uD@WOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784839667
OL,3,CNumber of Brits with eating disorders
OL,4,Cnearly trebles in less than 10 years
OL,6,F"Waiting lists have grown, demand for
OL,7,Fsupport has increased, and more people
OL,8,Fhave been reaching out to Beat
OL,9,Fdesperate for help.
OL,11,F"Professionals across the field have
OL,12,Falso been raising concerns that
OL,13,Fexisting prevalence estimates no
OL,14,Flonger reflected what they were seeing.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784839667
OL,3,CNumber of Brits with eating disorders
OL,4,Cnearly trebles in less than 10 years
OL,6,F"We've worked with researchers and
OL,7,Fstatisticians to look at the latest UK
OL,8,Fdata and eating disorders are likely
OL,9,Faffecting far more people than we
OL,10,Fpreviously knew. But perhaps the most
OL,11,Ftroubling finding is how much we still
OL,12,Fdon't know."
OL,14,FAn ITV News investigation in late 2025
OL,15,Ffound that the majority of eating
OL,16,Fdisorder clinics in the UK have
OL,17,Ftreated anorexia and bulimia patients,
OL,18,Fwho have previously used weight-loss
OL,19,Finjections.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784839667
OL,3,CNumber of Brits with eating disorders
OL,4,Cnearly trebles in less than 10 years
OL,6,FOne clinic told ITV News that 60% of
OL,7,Fits recent patients had used the so-
OL,8,Fcalled "skinny jabs".
OL,10,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,11,Fspokesperson said at the time:
OL,12,F"Obesity drugs can greatly benefit
OL,13,Fthose in real need, but they are
OL,14,Flicensed, prescription-only, medicines
OL,15,Fand should only be used by people who
OL,16,Fare eligible, under medical
OL,17,Fsupervision.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
