CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784839667
OL,3,CNumber of Brits with eating disorders
OL,4,Cnearly trebles in less than 10 years
OL,6,FLongley from Beat added: "The scale of
OL,7,Fthe problem is becoming clearer, but
OL,8,Ffor a condition likely affecting
OL,9,Fmillions of people, there has been far
OL,10,Ftoo little investment in research,
OL,11,Fprevention and ensuring people can
OL,12,Faccess the treatment they need without
OL,13,Fhaving to wait. This has to change."
OL,15,FDo you or someone you know suffer from
OL,16,Fan eating disorder? A number of
OL,17,Forganisations provide specialist
OL,18,Fadvice regarding eating disorders:
OL,20,F- Eating disorder specialist Beat can
OL,21,Fbe contacted at 0808 801 0677
OL,26,@nD@ZOUuD@dO]
