OL,3,CNumber of Brits with eating disorders
OL,4,Cnearly trebles in less than 10 years
OL,6,F- Family Lives can help families
OL,7,Fstruggling with loved ones suffering
OL,8,Ffrom an eating disorder. They can be
OL,9,Freached on WhatsApp at 07441 444125
OL,11,F- Young Minds specialises in
OL,12,Fsupporting parents with children's
OL,13,Fmental health. They can be contacted
OL,14,Fat 0808 802 5544.
OL,16,FNHS England also advises speaking to
OL,17,Fyour GP for advice on how to help at
OL,18,Fhome, and that it is helpful for the
OL,19,Fwhole family to be aware of someone's
OL,20,Fsituation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
